metadata.description: The Flow OG NFT is a collection of 100 unique NFTs - digital tokens stored on the Ethereum blockchain. Holding the Flow OG token signifies your status as a global citizen and urban explorer committed to creating a better world to live, work, and play. Connect this NFT to your account on the Flow app to unlock complimentary access to any location on Flow, including the best coworking spaces, gyms, spas, and experiences, as well as invite-only locations and other benefits granted exclusively to Flow OG token holders.
metadata.name: Flow OG
